@section Comments
@cindex comments

Forth supports two styles of comment; the traditional @i{in-line} comment,
@code{(} and its modern cousin, the @i{comment to end of line}; @code{\}.


@findex ( @var{ ( compilation 'ccc<close-paren>' -- ; run-time --   }  core,file
@cindex @code{(}
@kindex (
@format
