As an example, consider the following text, stored in a file @file{test.fs}:

@example
.( text-1)
: my-word
  ." text-2" cr
  .( text-3)
;

." text-4"

: my-char
  [char] ALPHABET emit
  char emit
;
@end example

When you load this code into Gforth, the following output is generated:

@example
